title: Santa Cruz Presents: Cruz'in Brazil
description: The Santa Cruz Team joins forces with Drop Dead Distribution to shred Brazil's savage concrete pits and stoke their fans out! Featuring: Emmanuel Guzman, Eric Dressen, Josh Borden, Justin Strubing with special guest and Creature Fiend, Milton Martinez.
